        "### Angle Between Vectors\n",
        "\n",
        "Using $\\cos\\theta = \\frac{\\mathbf{u} \\cdot \\mathbf{v}}{\\|\\mathbf{u}\\| \\, \\|\\mathbf{v}\\|}$:"
      ],
